org.gvsig.chart.swing

Interface ChartSwingManager

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Manager
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultChartSwingManager

    public interface ChartSwingManager
extends Manager
    This class is responsible of the management of the library's swing user interface. It is the swing library's main entry point, and provides all the services to manage library swing components.
    See Also:
    ChartWindowManager, JChartBlockPanel
